  "detailed_description": "3d Engineers lets you create constructions and mechanics in a physics environment.<br>Combine simple materials like beams, ropes, hydraulics, rockets aso to build architecture or vehicles from the ground up. Middle age or space is no topic as you are the inventor.<br>This game is beeing constantly extended, improved and updated.<br><br><strong>3d Engineers is coming with the full version of -3d.Bridges-</strong> (avaiable on Steam as well)<br>35 Leveltasks<br>8 Tutorial levels<br>8++ Playground levels",
  "about_the_game": "3d Engineers lets you create constructions and mechanics in a physics environment.<br>Combine simple materials like beams, ropes, hydraulics, rockets aso to build architecture or vehicles from the ground up. Middle age or space is no topic as you are the inventor.<br>This game is beeing constantly extended, improved and updated.<br><br><strong>3d Engineers is coming with the full version of -3d.Bridges-</strong> (avaiable on Steam as well)<br>35 Leveltasks<br>8 Tutorial levels<br>8++ Playground levels",
